al pay gaps, and their ideal pay gaps are even further from reality than those underestimates.", "pubmed-id": "26186109", "prism:coverDate": "2014-11-24", "prism:aggregationType": "Journal", "prism:url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84911212612", "dc:creator": {"author": [{"ce:given-name": "Sorapop", "preferred-name": {"ce:given-name": "Sorapop", "ce:initials": "S.", "ce:surname": "Kiatpongsan", "ce:indexed-name": "Kiatpongsan S."}, "@seq": "1", "ce:initials": "S.", "@_fa": "true", "affiliation": [{"@id": "60028190", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60028190"}, {"@id": "60138776", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60138776"}], "ce:surname": "Kiatpongsan", "@auid": "12645378300", "author-url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/12645378300", "ce:indexed-name": "Kiatpongsan S."}]}, "link": [{"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "self", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84911212612"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84911212612&origin=inward"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus-citedby", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/citedby.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84911212612&origin=inward"}], "source-id": "19700182323", "citedby-count": "188", "prism:volume": "9", "subtype": "ar", "dc:title": "How Much (More) Should CEOs Make? A Universal Desire for More Equal Pay", "openaccess": "2", "prism:issn": "17456924 17456916", "publishercopyright": "\u00a9 The Author(s) 2014.", "prism:issueIdentifier": "6", "subtypeDescription": "Article", "prism:publicationName": "Perspectives on Psychological Science", "prism:pageRange": "587-593", "prism:endingPage": "593", "openaccessFlag": null, "prism:doi": "10.1177/1745691614549773", "prism:startingPage": "587", "dc:identifier": "SCOPUS_ID:84911212612", "dc:publisher": "SAGE Publications Inc."}, "idxterms": {"mainterm": [{"$": "Commerce",